title: Falafelstern
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Falafel shop offering a varied range of falafel varieties on a plate or in a wrap. Has a vegan version of all the falafel dishes (with hummus). Try the fresh mint tea. Free Wi-Fi.
